name: Memory.
description:
By Vlas Belov 2022.

The shape of the head is a reference to a biological being, and the geometric black shapes are the memory.

Project from the "Biogeometry" series. AR Digital kinetic sculpture created in VR Oculus Medium, animation in Blender. Interactive 3D sculpture (glb). You can see in AR if you go to this page from your smartphone and press the AR button in the corner.
